        "name": "Refuse Pile",
        "subtype": "ability",
        "text": "When they're not in danger, an ofalth can spend 1 minute settling into a 10-foot pile that looks like a heap of garbage. Until the next time it takes an action, the ofalth gains a +2 circumstance bonus to AC. A creature that enters the area of the garbage heap or interacts with it must attempt a save against the ofalth's stench.",
        "type": "stat_block_section"
      }
